=== 销量 ===

《最终幻想X》获得媒体的高度讚譽以及高销量<ref name="mc" />。2000年PS2主機開始販售，2001年本作上市時史克威尔期望游戏在全球至少售出200万份，這是比前三部於PS平台的本傳都要少的數字，因為當時尚算PS2平台的初期，PS2主機的銷售數字還處於大幅落後前代PS主機的狀態<ref>{{cite web| title=The History of Final Fantasy| url=http://www.gamespot.com/features/vgs/universal/finalfantasy_hs/sec1_10.html| publisher=GameSpot| accessdate=2012-06-11| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20040606004506/http://www.gamespot.com/features/vgs/universal/finalfantasy_hs/sec1_10.html| archivedate=2004-06-06| deadurl=yes}}</ref>。然而游戏在日本的预售就超過140万套，创下當時游戏机RPG最快的销售纪录<ref>{{cite web | author=IGN Staff | date=2001-07-19 | title=Final Fantasy X Sells Like Crazy; World Not Shocked | url=http://ps2.ign.com/articles/096/096716p1.html | work=IGN | publisher=News Corporation | accessdate=2008-11-24 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/60eHjFM3z?url=http://ps2.ign.com/articles/096/096716p1.html | archive-date=2011-08-02 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="GWR08-RPG">{{cite book| last= |first= |editor= Craig Glenday| title= Guinness World Records Gamer's Edition 2008| url=https://archive.org/details/guinnessworldrec00guin_0| series= Guinness World Records| date= 2008-03-11| publisher= Guinness|isbn= 978-1-904994-21-3| pages= [https://archive.org/details/guinnessworldrec00guin_0/page/156 156]–167| chapter= Record Breaking Games: Role-Playing Games}}</ref>。發售4天後在日本出貨214萬套、售出192.6萬套，超过发售後經同样天數的《[[最终幻想VII|最终幻想VII]]》和《[[最终幻想IX|最终幻想IX]]》<ref>{{cite web | author=IGN Staff | date=2001-07-24 | title=Final Fantasy X Approaches 2 Million Copies Sold | url=http://ps2.ign.com/articles/096/096825p1.html | work=IGN | publisher=News Corporation | accessdate=2008-11-24 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67n4qLeFx?url=http://ps2.ign.com/articles/096/096825p1.html | archive-date=2012-05-20 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。《最终幻想X》是最早突破200万和400万销量的PlayStation 2游戏<ref>{{cite web | author=IGN Staff | date=2001-01-07 | title=FFX Tops Sales Charts | url=http://ps2.ign.com/articles/100/100730p1.html | publisher=IGN | accessdate=2008-11-24 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67n4vL7MM?url=http://ps2.ign.com/articles/100/100730p1.html | archive-date=2012-05-20 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | last=Varanini | first=Giancarlo | date=2002-01-30 | title=Final Fantasy X sales meet expectations | url=http://www.gamespot.com/ps2/rpg/finalfantasy10/news.html?sid=2843955 | work=GameSpot | publisher=News Corporation | accessdate=2008-11-24 | archive-date=2009-02-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090205212903/http://www.gamespot.com/ps2/rpg/finalfantasy10/news.html?sid=2843955 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，到2004年1月时售出660万套<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/ps2/rpg/finalfantasyx2/news_6086686.html |title=Final Fantasy X-2 sells a million |work=GameSpot |publisher=CBS Interactive |first=Justin |last=Calvert |date=2004-01-20 |accessdate=2008-11-24 |archive-date=2008-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081207092449/http://www.gamespot.com/ps2/rpg/finalfantasyx2/news_6086686.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在2009年10月时为第6畅销PlayStation 2平台游戏<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.cnet.com/pictures/images-the-top-10-best-selling-ps2-games/6/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2018-12-19 |archive-date=2019-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190502103357/https://www.cnet.com/pictures/images-the-top-10-best-selling-ps2-games/6/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。PS2版本累計在全球出貨超過850萬份<ref name="x1x2"/>，销量超过800萬份<ref name="PS2"/>。

=== 媒体评论 ===

日本和西方媒体都给游戏打出高分。日本电子游戏杂志《[[Fami通|Fami通]]》和《Fami通 PS2》给游戏打出接近满分的39/40<ref name="famitsu">{{cite web | author=IGN Staff | date=2001-07-13 | title=Final Fantasy X Gets Rated in Japan | url=http://ps2.ign.com/articles/096/096564p1.html | work=IGN | publisher=News Corporation | accessdate=2008-11-24 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/65Nw49r4d?url=http://ps2.ign.com/articles/096/096564p1.html | archive-date=2012-02-12 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>；而在《Fami通》2006年上半年的史上最佳游戏读者票选中，游戏获得首位<ref name="famitsureaders">{{cite web | author=Edge Staff | date=2006-03-03 | title=Japan Votes on All Time Top 100 | url=http://www.next-gen.biz/features/japan-votes-all-time-top-100 | work=Edge | accessdate=2008-11-24 | archive-date=2008-07-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080723051728/http://www.edge-online.com/features/japan-votes-all-time-top-100 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。另一日本游戏杂志《The Play Station》给游戏打出29/30。三本杂志特别称赞了游戏的情节、画面和影片<ref name="famitsu" />。游戏在[[GameRankings|GameRankings]]和[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]的汇总得分为91%和92/100<ref name="gr">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamerankings.com/htmlpages2/197344.asp?q=final%20fantasy%20x|title=Final Fantasy X Reviews|work=Game Rankings|publisher=CBS Interactive|accessdate=2008-11-24|archive-date=2009-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090111042537/http://www.gamerankings.com/htmlpages2/197344.asp?q=final%20fantasy%20x|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="mc">{{cite web | title=Final Fantasy X (ps2: 2001): Reviews | url=http://www.metacritic.com/games/platforms/ps2/finalfantasyx?q=Final%20Fantasy%20X | work=Metacritic | publisher=CBS Interactive | accessdate=2008-11-23 | archive-date=2008-09-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080917185724/http://www.metacritic.com/games/platforms/ps2/finalfantasyx?q=Final%20Fantasy%20X | dead-url=no }}</ref>。制作人[[桥本真司|桥本真司]]称总体评价“极好”，得到媒体的称赞和奖项<ref name="cvg">{{cite web|url=http://m.computerandvideogames.com/27968/interviews/interview-square-invades-london?ns_campaign=mobile-yml&ns_mchannel=mobile-site&ns_source=cvg&ns_linkname=0&ns_fee=0|publisher=Computer and Video Games|date=2002-04-15|author=Minkley, Johnny|title=Interview: Square invades London|accessdate=2013-04-14|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130414084205/http://m.computerandvideogames.com/27968/interviews/interview-square-invades-london?ns_campaign=mobile-yml&ns_mchannel=mobile-site&ns_source=cvg&ns_linkname=0&ns_fee=0|archivedate=2013-04-14|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

[[IGN|IGN]]的大卫·史密斯对配音演员和游戏性的革新——特别是变化的战斗和召唤系统、可以选择在战斗中更换队员，以及角色发展和物品管理系统——表示称赞。他们亦称《最终幻想X》的图形在前作之上做了一切可能改进，游戏总的说来“是系列最好看的游戏，也大概是最好玩的游戏”<ref name="IGN">{{cite web | date=2001-12-18 | title=Final Fantasy X Review | url=http://ps2.ign.com/articles/164/164008p1.html | work=IGN | publisher=News Corporation | first=David | last=Smith | accessdate=2008-11-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20020215065605/http://ps2.ign.com/articles/164/164008p1.html | archive-date=2002-02-15 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]的[[格雷格·卡萨文|格雷格·卡萨文]]赞扬了游戏的情节，谓其相当复杂、结局令人满意、通过有感染力的主角提达避免了角色扮演游戏的俗套。他还称赞音乐“多样且在各种游戏场面都很应景”<ref name="GSpot">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/ps2/rpg/finalfantasy10/review.html?om_act=convert&om_clk=tabs&tag=tabs;reviews |title=Final Fantasy X Review |first=Greg |last=Kasavin |date=2001-12-14 |work=GameSpot |publisher=CBS Interactive |accessdate=2008-11-23 |archive-date=2009-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090212230738/http://www.gamespot.com/ps2/rpg/finalfantasy10/review.html?om_act=convert&om_clk=tabs&tag=tabs%3Breviews |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
[[GamePro|GamePro]]同样对角色发展系统和战斗系统表示称赞，称其为“系列中的两大革新”<ref name="Gpro">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamepro.com/article/reviews/19160/final-fantasy-x/|title=GamePro: Final Fantasy X|first=Mike|last=Weigand|date=2001-12-14|publisher=GamePro|accessdate=2010-07-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100927063641/http://www.gamepro.com/article/reviews/19160/final-fantasy-x/|archivedate=2010-09-27|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。GameSpot的雷蒙德·帕迪拉夸赞游戏画面“拔尖”，同时也对角色模型、背景、过场和动画表示肯定<ref name="GSpy">{{cite web |url=http://ps2.gamespy.com/playstation-2/final-fantasy-x/539181p1.html |title=Final Fantasy X Review |publisher=GameSpy |first=Raymond |last=Padilla |date=2001-12-15 |accessdate=2008-11-20 |archive-date=2012-07-15 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20120715100636/http://ps2.gamespy.com/playstation-2/final-fantasy-x/539181p1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Game_Revolution|Game Revolution]]称赞配音“在平均之上”，并称赞音乐“充足”<ref name="Grev">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamerevolution.com/review/ps2/final-fantasy-x|title=GameRevolution: Final Fantasy X|first=Johnny|last=Liu|date=2001-12-01|work=Game Revolution|publisher=Atomic Online|accessdate=2010-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091102070510/http://www.gamerevolution.com/review/ps2/final-fantasy-x|archive-date=2009-11-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

《[[Edge_(杂志)|Edge]]》给予游戏相当的低分，批评游戏在诸多方面冗长且无新意，称对话以提达的为首“令人生厌”<ref name="edge">{{cite book | year=2002 | title=Edge February 2002; issue 107 | pages=76–77 | publisher=Future plc}}</ref>。《Game Informer》的安德鲁·莱内尔批评游戏线性，玩家再无法通过骑[[陆行鸟|陆行鸟]]或操控飞空艇环游世界<ref name="GI">{{cite web|url=http://www.gameinformer.com/Games/Review/200201/R03.0801.1256.47994.htm|title=Final Fantasy X|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20050224045521/http://www.gameinformer.com/Games/Review/200201/R03.0801.1256.47994.htm|archivedate=2005-02-24|first=Justin|last=Leeper|work=Game Informer|accessdate=2008-11-23|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]的汤姆·布拉姆韦尔称游戏解密部分“令人沮丧”且“多余”，虽然幻光球盘“看着不错”，但占据游戏太多了<ref name="EuroG">{{cite web |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/article.php?article_id=3204 |title=Final Fantasy X Review |first=Tom |last=Bramwell |date=2002-06-16 |publisher=Eurogamer |accessdate=2008-11-23 |archive-date=2008-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081207144050/http://www.eurogamer.net/article.php?article_id=3204 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《GamePro》对游戏的线性表示肯定，称能让无意于支线任务或小游戏者直通结局<ref name="Gpro" />。Game Revolution对游戏过场无法跳过表示不满，并认为其中一些太长了<ref name="Grev" />。

=== 奖项 ===

《最终幻想X》获得2001－2002年度[[日本游戏大奖|日本游戏大奖]]之最佳游戏奖<ref name="cesa">{{cite web | title=最優秀賞は「FF10」!! 「第6回 CESA GAME AWARDS」授賞式 | url=http://www.gpara.com/news/02/10/news200210280717.htm | publisher=GPARA.COM | accessdate=2009-05-28 | archive-date=2011-08-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110826011503/http://www.gpara.com/news/02/10/news200210280717.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2001年GameSpot的“最佳与最劣奖”中，游戏获得“年度十大电子游戏”分类的第7名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/gamespot/features/video/bestof_2001/p6_02.html|title=The Best and Worst of 2001|work=GameSpot|publisher=CBS Interactive|accessdate=2010-07-06|archive-date=2012-05-20|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67n51slHZ?url=http://www.gamespot.com/gamespot/features/video/bestof_2001/p6_02.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《最终幻想X》成为IGN 2007年“史上25大PS2游戏”的第5名以及“史上10大最佳画面PS游戏”的第6名<ref>{{cite web | author=IGN PlayStation Team | date=2007-03-16 | url=http://ps2.ign.com/articles/772/772296p3.html | title=The Top 25 PS2 Games of All Time | work=IGN | publisher=News Corporation | accessdate=2008-11-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090228201618/http://ps2.ign.com/articles/772/772296p3.html | archive-date=2009-02-28 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web| date=2010-05-07| url=http://ps2.ign.com/articles/606/606189p2.html| title=The Top 10 Best Looking PS2 Games of All Time| publisher=IGN| accessdate=2010-06-29| archive-date=2010-06-29| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100629140052/http://ps2.ign.com/articles/606/606189p2.html| dead-url=no}}</ref>。游戏在GameSpy的史上25大PlayStation 2游戏榜单中排名第21<ref>{{cite web| date=2007-03-16| url=http://ps2.gamespy.com/articles/693/693430p6.html| page=6| title=Top 25 PS2 Games| publisher=GameSpy| accessdate=2010-07-05| archive-date=2010-07-12| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100712053758/http://ps2.gamespy.com/articles/693/693430p6.html| dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]将游戏结局列为第3杰出的电子游戏桥段，而IGN将其列为第五大预渲染过场动画<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.1up.com/do/feature?cId=3168011|title=Top 5 Videogame Spoilers|author=Sharkey, Scott; Betenhausen, Shane; Nelson, Michael|publisher=1UP.com|accessdate=2010-06-02|archive-date=2012-07-16|archive-url=https://archive.today/20120716055944/http://www.1up.com/features/top-5-spoilers|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | date=2006-06-20 | url=http://ps2.ign.com/articles/713/713671p1.html | title=The Top 10 Tuesday: Best Pre-Rendered Cutscenes | work=IGN | publisher=News Corporation | accessdate=2010-06-29 | archive-date=2011-06-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629133657/http://ps2.ign.com/articles/713/713671p1.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。在IGN 2006年的最佳电子游戏读者票选中，游戏获得第60名<ref>{{cite web | date=2006-06-20 | url=http://top100.ign.com/2006/051-060.html | title=Readers' Picks Top 100 Games | work=IGN | publisher=News Corporation | accessdate=2010-06-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100814180057/http://top100.ign.com/2006/051-060.html | archive-date=2010-08-14 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。游戏还被[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]选为20款必备日式角色扮演游戏之一<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/3581/a_japanese_rpg_primer_the_.php?page=15 |page=15 |title=A Japanese RPG Primer – Final Fantasy X |author=Kalata, Kurt |date=2008-03-19 |publisher=Gamasutra |accessdate=2009-11-25 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303194234/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/3581/a_japanese_rpg_primer_the_.php?page=15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。游戏还登上《[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]》“史上200大电子游戏”榜单的第43位<ref name="GItop200">{{cite journal|author=''Game Informer'' staff|date=December 2009|title=The Top 200 Games of All Time|work=Game Informer|issue=200|pages=44–79}}</ref>。《最终幻想X》是[[GameFAQs|GameFAQs]]2004年选出的最伟大的电子游戏之一<ref>{{cite web | title=Spring 2004: Best. Game. Ever | url=http://www.gamefaqs.com/features/contest/c04spr | publisher=GameFAQs | accessdate=2008-07-16 | archive-date=2009-02-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090209040851/http://www.gamefaqs.com/features/contest/c04spr | dead-url=no }}</ref>，2005年11月又在“史上最佳游戏”票选中获得第12名<ref>{{cite web | title=Fall 2005: 10-Year Anniversary Contest—The 10 Best Games Ever | url=http://www.gamefaqs.com/features/contest/top10 | publisher=GameFAQs | accessdate=2008-07-16 | archive-date=2009-03-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090316073741/http://www.gamefaqs.com/features/contest/top10 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。在系列横评中，[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]]和IGN都将《最终幻想X》排在第4名<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamesradar.com/f/the-top-7-best-final-fantasy-games/a-201002261573698036/p-2 |page=2 |title=The Top 7... Best Final Fantasy games |date=2008-03-19 |publisher=GamesRadar |accessdate=2010-07-05 |archive-date=2011-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110615200029/http://www.gamesradar.com/f/the-top-7-best-final-fantasy-games/a-201002261573698036/p-2 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://ps3.ign.com/articles/105/1057079p1.html|page=1|title=Ranking the Final Fantasy Series|date=2009-12-09|work=IGN|publisher=News Corporation|accessdate=2010-07-05|archive-date=2010-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100615133046/http://ps3.ign.com/articles/105/1057079p1.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。在2003年举办的第6届[[互动成就奖|互动成就奖]]中，游戏被提名“动画杰出成就奖”和“年度游戏机角色扮演游戏”<ref>{{cite web | title=AIAS ANNUAL AWARDS > 6TH ANNUAL AWARDS | url=http://www.interactive.org/awards/2003_6th_awards.asp | publisher=Academy of Interactive Arts & Sciences | accessdate=2008-11-19 | archive-date=2010-10-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101023023559/http://www.interactive.org/awards/2003_6th_awards.asp | dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[吉尼斯世界纪录|吉尼斯世界纪录]]在2007年年末将《最终幻想X》认证为第9畅销RPG<ref name="GWR08-RPG" />。游戏在2001年被GameFAQs读者投票选为年度游戏<ref name="gamefaqs">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamefaqs.com/poll/index.html?poll=776|title=BEST OF 2001: Overall Game of the Year|publisher=GameFaqs|accessdate=2012-01-06|archive-date=2011-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111219120012/http://www.gamefaqs.com/poll/index.html?poll=776|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在《电击》杂志2008年举办的读者投票中，游戏获选成为史上第二佳游戏<ref name="kotakudengeki">{{cite web | first=Brian | last=Ashcraft | date=2008-03-06 | title=Dengeki Readers Say Fav 2007 Game, Fav of All Time | url=http://kotaku.com/364353/dengeki-readers-say-fav-2007-game-fav-of-all-time | publisher=Kotaku | accessdate=2008-03-29 | archive-date=2008-03-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080328132737/http://kotaku.com/364353/dengeki-readers-say-fav-2007-game-fav-of-all-time | dead-url=no }}</ref>。游戏还获得《Fami通》和《电击》史上最催泪游戏投票的首位<ref name="Famitsupollsec">{{cite web|last=Romano|first=Sal|url=http://gematsu.com/2011/12/famitsus-top-20-list-of-tear-inducing-games|publisher=Gematsu|title=Famitsu's top 20 list of tear-inducing games|date=2011-12-29|accessdate=2012-02-24|archive-date=2012-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120306155226/http://gematsu.com/2011/12/famitsus-top-20-list-of-tear-inducing-games|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=【アンケート結果発表】感動して泣いてしまったゲームはありますか?|trans_title=(Survey results) Are There Emotional Games That Made You Cry?|url=http://news.dengeki.com/elem/000/000/113/113442/|publisher=ASCII Media Works|date=2008-10-15|accessdate=2012-05-07|language=ja|archive-date=2012-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120419012624/http://news.dengeki.com/elem/000/000/113/113442/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。提达和尤娜主要因个性和彼此浪漫关系而成为受欢迎的游戏角色<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamezone.com/editorials/top-10-final-fantasy-characters|title=Top 10 Final Fantasy Characters|author=Hooker, Heath|publisher=GameZone|accessdate=2012-06-14|archive-date=2012-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120509194555/http://www.gamezone.com/editorials/top-10-final-fantasy-characters|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="GreatLove">{{cite web| url = http://www.gamespot.com/features/6144012/p-5.html| title = Great Loves - Features at GameSpot| work = GameSpot| publisher = CBS Interactive| date = 2006-02-14| accessdate = 2008-03-13| archive-date = 2007-05-18| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070518135027/http://www.gamespot.com/features/6144012/p-5.html| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.gamesradar.com/f/the-14-best-videogame-couples/a-20100212134311112031/p-3| title = The 14 Best Videogame Couples| publisher = GamesRadar| date = 2006-02-14| accessdate = 2010-02-14| archive-date = 2011-06-15| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110615185515/http://www.gamesradar.com/f/the-14-best-videogame-couples/a-20100212134311112031/p-3| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

== 影响 ==

{{Further|最终幻想X-2}}随着PS2版《最终幻想X》的商业成功，2003年史克威尔艾尼克斯繼續在PS2平台上发行了后传《[[最终幻想X-2|最终幻想X-2]]》<ref name="FFX-2">{{cite web | last=Dunham | first=Jeremy | date=2003-11-24 | title=Final Fantasy X-2 Developer Interview | url=http://ps2.ign.com/articles/442/442025p1.html | work=IGN | publisher=News Corporation | accessdate=2008-11-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20031226004159/http://ps2.ign.com/articles/442/442025p1.html?fromint=1 | archive-date=2003-12-26 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。续作设定于《最终幻想X》结局的两年后，以新冲突和难题为情节，并解释了原游戏留下的未解结局。虽然续作超過540万的销量<ref name="x1x2">{{Cite web |url=https://asia.playstation.com/hk/en/newsdetail?id=235 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2018-12-18 |archive-date=2018-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181218145852/https://asia.playstation.com/hk/en/newsdetail?id=235 |dead-url=no }}</ref>的销量不如前作的超過800万，但仍被视为商业成功。因为作品的人气，[[北濑佳范|北濑佳范]]和[[野岛一成|野岛一成]]决定在《最终幻想X》和《最终幻想VII》——另一畅销最终幻想游戏——中建立相关情节<ref>{{cite book | year=2001 | editor=Studio BentStuff | title=Final Fantasy X Ultimania Ω | page=191 | language = ja | publisher=DigiCube | isbn=4-88787-021-3}}</ref>。2013年在《高清重制版》发行后，野岛称他希望看到《最终幻想X》的第二部续作，且如果有需求，这并非不可能<ref name="PossibleX3">{{cite web|url=http://www.siliconera.com/2013/12/26/final-fantasy-x-scenario-writer-possibility-final-fantasy-x-3/|title=Final Fantasy X Scenario Writer On The Possibility Of Final Fantasy X-3|author=Sato|publisher=Siliconera|date=2013-12-26|accessdate=2013-12-26|archive-date=2013-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131227000246/http://www.siliconera.com/2013/12/26/final-fantasy-x-scenario-writer-possibility-final-fantasy-x-3/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《最终幻想X》通过配音和细致的面部表情达到的逼真情绪描绘优势已成为系列的基本特征，后来《最终幻想X-2》等作品也采用这种开发。以全程即时3D环境取代世界地图也成为系列标准之一，《最终幻想XI》、《[[最终幻想XII|XII]]》、《[[最终幻想XIII|XIII]]》及续作、《[[最终幻想XIV|XIV]]》和《[[最终幻想XV|XV]]》都采用这种方式。《最终幻想X》可被视作3D RPG地图的先导<ref name="GT-FFRetrospectiveVII">{{cite web| url = http://www.gametrailers.com/video/part-vii-final-fantasy/24248| title = Final Fantasy Retrospective Part VII| publisher = GameTrailers| date = 2007-08-28| accessdate = 2009-04-06| archive-date = 2009-06-22| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090622021020/http://www.gametrailers.com/video/part-vii-final-fantasy/24248| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

